cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.IR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to classify the stance expressed in tweets during rumourous conversations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with multi-task learning, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Software Engineering). The paper also uses Gaussian Processes, which is a machine learning technique falling under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
